snippet.title: The Secret Elevator Remastered | mobile game
snippet.description:
The Secret Elevator Remastered is a short first-person narrative adventure with horror and puzzle elements for iOS. 

It is a psychological story about a man facing tragedy and overcoming difficulties within himself.

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-secret-elevator-remastered/id1094038347
Google Play: @pps/details.free
RuStore: https://apps.rustore.ru/app/tser.omolgame
